  "2026-02-17T23:42:24.565Z",cursor-agent,"Updated docs-first contracts before code behavior changes: command surface scoped to v0.1, release-ready structure defined, sandbox PM_PATH test safety codified, and release checklist added."
  "2026-02-18T00:16:09.388Z",cursor-agent,Updated README installation contract with explicit npm update command and installer idempotent update guidance.
  "2026-02-18T00:17:34.704Z",cursor-agent,Added AGENTS guidance to avoid linking pm test-all as an item-level test command to prevent recursive orchestration loops.
